osition:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A7%80%EB%82%A8%EC%97%90-%EB%94%B0%EB%9D%BC-%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0-%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0%EA%B3%BC-%EB%8B%A4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%9C%BC%EB%8B%88-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98-%EB%B0%94%EB%9E%8D%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"시간이 지남에 따라 최신 기술과 다를 수 있으니 주의 바랍니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>시간이 지남에 따라 최신 기술과 다를 수 있으니 주의 바랍니다.</h4>\n<hr>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/2cefc/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.306748466257666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thumbnail\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/a6d36/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/222b7/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 163w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/ff46a/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 325w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/a6d36/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 650w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/e548f/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 975w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/3c492/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 1300w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/2cefc/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h1 id=\"thymeleaf에서-조건문-사용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#thymeleaf%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EB%AC%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"thymeleaf에서 조건문 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thymeleaf에서 조건문 사용하기</h1>\n<p>Thymeleaf를 사용하다 보면 서버측의 데이터에 대한 분기 조건이 필요할 경우가 있습니다.<br>\n이번 포스팅에서는 if와 else를 사용하는 것에 대해 알아보겠습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"if-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#if-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"if 문 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>if 문</h2>\n<p>Thymeleaf에서 if문은 다음과 같이 사용합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>if</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${pageMaker.isPrev()}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>th:if</strong> 문법으로 사용하는데 태그는 li 뿐만이 아닌 div등에 사용하여 조건이 맞는 경우 화면에 보여줄 수도 있고, 감출 수도 있습니다.<br>\n만약 다중 조건을 찾아야 하는 경우에는 다음과 같이 사용하기도 합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>if</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${account.getAccountStatus().toString().equals('ACTIVE')}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>재직중<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>if</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${account.getAccountStatus().toString().equals('VACATION')}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>휴가<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>if</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${account.getAccountStatus().toString().equals('ETC')}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>기타<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"else-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#else-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"else 문 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>else 문</h2>\n<p>다중 if문으로도 체크 가능하지만 그 외의 값을 체크할 때 else를 사용하는데, else는 thymeleaf에서는 다른 속성인 <strong>th:unless</strong>를 사용합니다.\n사용 예제 코드는 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>if</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${dto.getFileStatus().toString()} == 'ON_SUMMER'<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>text</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${dto.getUploadName()} + ' (에디터 첨부파일)'<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>unless</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${dto.getFileStatus().toString()} == 'ON_SUMMER'<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">th:</span>text</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>${dto.getUploadName()}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 예제처럼 <strong>th:unless</strong>는 if문과 조건이 동일하지만 사실 if조건과 다른 조건인 경우를 검색하게 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toc\"><pre class=\"language-toc\"><code class=\"language-toc\"></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98\">주의</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AC%B8%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80-%EA%B3%BC%EA%B1%B0-hexo-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-2018-02-18-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EB%8F%99%EB%90%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">이 문건은 과거 Hexo 블로그 (2018-02-18) 에서 이동된 문서입니다.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#thymeleaf%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EB%AC%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Thymeleaf에서 조건문 사용하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#if-%EB%AC%B8\">if 문</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#else-%EB%AC%B8\">else 문</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Thymeleaf에서 if else 조건문 사용법","description":null,"date":"February 18, 2018","tags":["Thymeleaf"],"series":"Thymeleaf","previewImage":"thymeleaf_logo.png","isPrivate":null,"writer":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/thymeleaf/180217_thymeleaf-layout-dialect/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Thymeleaf에서 thymeleaf-layout-dialect 소개","isPrivate":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring_spring-boot/180218_spring-parameter/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring에서 @RequestParam과 @PathVariable","isPrivate":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"9a0c2520-d90e-5e3a-9b5a-2f60eaf6d080","previousPostId":"dcc6a06c-6b00-5869-ba81-e76e3f53e7e2","nextPostId":"838421f9-3007-5752-b14f-6aef83e69495"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}